cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper focuses on automatic acquisition and analysis of photographs and webcam images, which involves computer vision techniques such as image processing and object recognition. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia): The proposed system involves multimedia content (photographs and webcam images) and a web portal for photo-sharing. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The system may involve information retrieval techniques to extract relevant visual content from a large pool of user-generated content. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks): The web portal acts as a social web site for photo-sharing, which involves social network analysis and user behavior modeling. 
- cs.GR (Graphics): The system may involve graphics techniques for visualizing and presenting the acquired data.
